0.2ß
 Added the About and Quit Menus.
 Created the About window.
 Fixed a few typos.
 Changed the Logo to pxman's one. 
 Fixed the handling of DisplayText Packet.
 Now appicon for Skully is skully.info.
 About window can be opened from the skullylogo.
 Modified slightly the gui to correct display problems with
  Frame_Title in strings gadgets.
 Added his name in the about window.
 Changed the frame of the text.
 Made the log list be multicolumn.
 Rewrote the makefile to handle more easily debug releases.
 Added support for displaytxt command.
 Modified the AddCallInd decoding to display the text in the log list.
 Added MUI bubles to most gadgets.
 Now at the initial settings load, the status bar displays 'settings loaded'.
 Managed the occurency of unexpected packet (traces it).
 Changed the automaton for the disconnection states. 
 Now waits for the ACK.
 Now Warn uniconifies the application.
 Added MUIA_Application_SingleTask, TRUE
 Removed the code that didn't rely on notification of the sknet state.
 Added the Compiledate in the version string.
 Skully crashed when run without a tcp stack.
 Added a status line modification to reflect a save and load.
 Wrote the (short (!!)) amigaguide.
 Wrote the readme.
 Changed 'Log' Tab to 'Traffic'
 
0.1aß:

 Skully didn't open the correct libraries and crashed awfully after a 
 sequence of connect/disconnect. 
 When leaving with the close gadget, bsdsocket.library was not closed if
 skully was online.
 Removed the timeout requester (hi fab :).
 Added logs.
 Changed the sknet class so that it can be notified on it's internal state.
 Fixed a few retransmission bugs

0.1ß:
 initial beta release.

