 Here are the improvement that are allready planned for Skully:

  GUI
- Localization of the program  (!!) (at least in french)
- Pass to NListView
- add a logfile option to make the tracing of other versions easier.
- network activity lamp in the GUI.                            
- optional 'minipanel' that displays the state of the skully automaton
  and other infos.
- Help Bubbles as an option.
- About MUI menu item
- Clean the proto-log as an option on 'Connect' action.

  NETWORK
- support for the telnet + http/1.1 connection/authentif method
- optional offline/online of the interface at online time      
- check for the interface before calling send and on timeouts. 

- Log the ascending/descending traffic on a monthly basis. 
  Most providers (have/will) set up a limit to transfer amounts.
- add an option to make skully try to reconnect if the stack is set offline

  OTHER
- Rexx Support in both senses.
- French Amigaguide doc (!!)

  AND FINALLY 

  Here are the improvements that I will do if I can have contacts with
  other users.

- real turboline-ras support if I can find a beta tester
- support for different version of ras protocol "" ""
- provide default configurations for users from different places

 Suggestions are welcomed.

